== 評價 ==
遊戲於歐洲和美國普遍獲得正面評價。GameRankings基於28則評論而為遊戲的PS3版本給予82.39之平均分<ref>[http://www.gamerankings.com/ps3/943325-eternal-sonata/index.html Eternal Sonata – PlayStation 3] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/ps3/943325-eternal-sonata/index.html |date=20191209011503 }}, [[GameRankings|GameRankings]]</ref>Xbox360版本則基於57則評論而給予80.32分<ref>[http://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/934162-eternal-sonata/index.html Eternal Sonata – X box 360] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/934162-eternal-sonata/index.html |date=20191209015659 }}, [[GameRankings|GameRankings]]</ref>。Metacritic基於34則評論而為PS3版本給予80之平均分<ref>[http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/eternal-sonata Eternal Sonata – PlayStation 3] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/eternal-sonata |date=20200907082218 }}, [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]</ref>，Xbox 360版本則按53則評論而給予79分<ref>[http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/xbox360/eternalsonata?q=eternal%20sonata Eternal Sonata – Xbox 360] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/xbox360/eternalsonata?q=eternal%20sonata |date=20081210170120 }}, [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]</ref>。GameSpot以十分滿分中給予8.5分，認為遊戲視覺設計美觀、配樂出色、戰鬥系統新穎而且角色豐富，但承認故事發展過於線性<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/rpg/trustybellchopinnoyume/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review|title=DeadLink|accessdate=August 6, 2007|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208034750/http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/rpg/trustybellchopinnoyume/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=gssummary&tag=summary;read-review|archivedate=2008年12月8日}}</ref>。 IGN以十分滿分中給予Xbox 360版8.3分，認為遊戲視覺效果是Xbox 360遊戲中數一數二、戰鬥出眾、原聲大碟非常出色、故事也成功讓玩家認識了蕭邦，但也認為故事過短且缺乏世界探索<ref>{{cite web|url=http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/819/819923p1.html|title=Eternal Sonata Review|publisher=IGN.com|date=|accessdate=2008-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218160003/http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/819/819923p1.html|archive-date=2008-12-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；PS3版則給予8.7分，指出故事有所擴展、加入了新角色及其他遊戲內容<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ps3.ign.com/articles/923/923711p1.html|title=Eternal Sonata Review (PS3)|publisher=IGN.com|date=|accessdate=2008-12-18|archive-date=2012-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120817060739/http://ps3.ign.com/articles/923/923711p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。X-Play以五分滿中分給予3分，對戰鬥、配樂和視覺效果予以表揚但認為小遊戲和傳統RPG元素過多、以及故事欠佳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/reviews/1638/Eternal_Sonata.html|title=X-Play Eternal Sonata Review|publisher=G4tv.com|date=|accessdate=2008-12-18|archive-date=2017-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228040846/http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/reviews/1638/Eternal_Sonata.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Eludamos Journal for Computer Game Culture人士Johansen Quijano-Cruz認為遊戲以藝術與文學的角度而言是出色的RPG作品，尤其是故事內容對現今社會作出了強而有力的批判。<ref>Johansen Quijano-Cruz (2009), [http://journals.sfu.ca/eludamos/index.php/eludamos/article/viewArticle/68/131 Chopin's Dream as Reality – A Critical Reading of Eternal Sonata] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.sfu.ca/eludamos/index.php/eludamos/article/viewArticle/68/131 |date=20120312134354 }}, ''Eludamos Journal for Computer Game Culture'' '''3''' (2), pp. 209–218</ref>{{-}}

